# Oven Baked White Fish With Tomatoes

Based on [https://www.budgetbytes.com/easy-oven-baked-fish-with-tomatoes/...](https://www.budgetbytes.com/easy-oven-baked-fish-with-tomatoes) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20250821131959/https://www.budgetbytes.com/easy-oven-baked-fish-with-tomatoes/)). Recommended by Becky and Will. Enhanced with aromatics, crispy topping, and flavor depth

